PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778234502
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'much-loved'
OL,4,Cbiker after a fatal crash
OL,6,FDavid's partner described him as "my
OL,7,Ffiance, my best friend, stepdad to my
OL,8,Fdaughter... an absolute gentleman and
OL,9,Floved by so many people.
OL,11,F"He would light up any room with his
OL,12,Fbig smile and would do anything for
OL,13,Fanyone, no matter how small. You are
OL,14,Fgoing to be missed so, so much. It's
OL,15,Fleft a massive hole in our lives; it
OL,16,Fwill never be the same without you
OL,17,Faround.
OL,19,F"I love you Dave so much, sleep tight
OL,20,Fbabe."
OL,26,@nD@bOUoD@FrrsD@AOU{D@AOU|D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
