FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778234502
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'much-loved'
OL,4,Cbiker after a fatal crash
OL,6,FHis children said: "Even after death,
OL,7,Fwe will always find a way to ride
OL,8,Fagain.
OL,10,F"Your loving children."
OL,12,FDavid's twin sister added, "We are
OL,13,Ftruly heartbroken by the tragic death
OL,14,Fof our beloved David. He had
OL,15,Feverything to live for - a much-loved
OL,16,Fson and brother.
OL,18,F"We take great comfort knowing you're
OL,19,Fback with your mum now.
OL,26,@nD@TOUrD@AOUrD@WO]tD@\OUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
