PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778234502
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'much-loved'
OL,4,Cbiker after a fatal crash
OL,6,F"Thank you for the outpouring of
OL,7,Fcondolences from not only friends and
OL,8,Ffamily, but strangers and the biker
OL,9,Fcommunity that adored David."
OL,11,FOfficers from the Serious Collisions
OL,12,FInvestigation Unit (SCIU) are
OL,13,Fcontinuing to appeal for witnesses and
OL,14,Fanyone with CCTV, dashcam or mobile
OL,15,Fphone footage of the incident or the
OL,16,Fmoments leading up to it.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@]O]
